data.about: Luxehues is an exclusive online portal offering best value, authentic, luxury designer products, both global and indian with 100% Insurance & free shipping
data.name: Luxehues
data.description:
Starting out with a modest 30 partner brands and high hopes, today Luxehues.com lists over 350 global brands across multiple categories.

We get you products straight from the brands. Working directly with Principal Brands, we are able to give you the promise of better value, quality and authenticity with every purchase.

Luxehues is part of the Luxury Hues Group, a leading player in the luxury space with its businesses focused on partnering with organizations offering lifestyle products and services to affluent customers. The group companies include Quintessentially Lifestyle Services India which is a part of Quintessentially UK, the world’s leading luxury lifestyle group with 66 offices across the globe.

Luxehues.com is strongly backed by Reliance Capital Ltd.
